text: Corral de Piedra Palustrine Wetland (), is a protected area in Costa Rica, managed under the Tempisque Conservation Area, it was created in 1994 by decree 22898-MIRENEM. == References == Category:Costa Rica Category:Protected areas Category:Nature reserves in Costa Rica Category:Protected areas established in 1994
title: Corral de Piedra Palustrine Wetland
